Conseco Industries Ltd saidan order of confirmation of its reorganization plan has beensigned in its Chapter 11 bankruptcy proceedings, terminatingits status as a debtor in possession.    Conseco said under the plan, general creditors anddebenture holders will receive 27 pct of their claims over atwo-year period and president Charles J. Trainor will pay250,000 dlrs for 2,500,000 new shares.    The company said debenture holders will have 30 days toconvert their debentures into common shares.    It said it has arranged for two mln dlrs of new bankfinancing. Reuter&#3;